-- QB AIMBOT
-- Improvements v2:
-- * Iterative prediction: solve -> re-predict 3 times for tight accuracy
-- * Velocity smoothing uses per-frame EMA with adaptive gain (fast when vel changes a lot)
-- * qb_gMag exposed per throw-type so lobs use lower gravity feel (higher arc)
-- * Angle solver now steps by 0.5deg instead of 1deg for finer resolution
-- * qbExec always re-solves fresh at fire time (not stale RenderStepped calc)
-- * qbDoThrow uses actual head pos at fire moment, not cached
-- * Auto-power reads game bar as first priority when enabled = false
-- * Anti-overthrow clamp: if solved power > 92, walk angle up to bring it down
-- * Target selector: prefers closest-to-camera AND closest in distance (blended)
-- ================================================================
